originalText.text: Had a great experience with Dr. Park! I absolutely hate going to the dentist but she makes you feel comfortable, is gentle, and also takes the time to explain everything each step of the way. What I appreciate the most is that she genuinely cares about your long-term dental health and not just looking to make a quick fix. She is def my go to dentist going forward - highly recommend!! ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

originalText.text:
I want to  start by saying that these guys are fantastic and super honest.
I had a retreat root canal at the office from another practice somewhere else in the city, they were upfront and told me that I could also choose for the option to remove the tooth and put an implant instead of trying to save the tooth, as there was a risk of not working.
I should have probably chosen to extract the tooth in fact. As the retreat didn't work and got infected. Dr Wang was extremely generous and gave me a credit towards the extraction and the implant which is so generous of him. I highly recommend the practice, they are really good and professional. you should definitely go there for all your teeth matters.

originalText.text:
I am incredibly grateful for the exceptional care I received from Dr. Park and her assistant Joanna at 209 NYC Dental over the past six months. After having my front tooth pulled, Dr. Park worked tirelessly to craft a fake tooth that not only met my functional needs but also looked cosmetically perfect. Her attention to detail and commitment to excellence were evident in every step of the process.

Dr. Park's genuine compassion and willingness to accommodate my schedule made the entire experience comfortable and reassuring. Her professionalism and kindness created a warm atmosphere that eased any apprehension I had.

Thanks to Dr. Park's expertise, I now smile with confidence. I feel fortunate to have her as my dentist at 209 NYC Dental. I wholeheartedly recommend Dr. Park to anyone seeking top-notch dental care.

originalText.text:
Over the past year, I've been a patient of Dr. Stella Park, and I've consistently had positive experiences. Dr. Park's extensive knowledge is apparent in her thorough approach to dental care. What distinguishes her is her patient-centric attitude, making me feel listened to and cared for during each appointment.
Dr. Park's gentle technique during multiple fillings was notable and greatly appreciated, minimizing discomfort and creating a more pleasant experience.
I value the emphasis on patient education probably the most and Dr. Park took the time to explain procedures and provided valuable tips for maintaining oral health. I highly recommend Dr. Stella Park for those in search of expert care with a compassionate approach.
The meticulous routine cleanings by hygienist Oksana contribute to a comprehensive oral health routine.
The entire team at the office fosters a welcoming atmosphere, enhancing the overall dental visit. From scheduling appointments to the actual procedures, the efficiency and professionalism are commendable.
